---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Events">

  <div class="relative-z">
    <div class="hero-section">
      <div class="container hero-content text-center">
        <h1 class="animate-fade-up">Our <span class="text-primary">Events</span></h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle animate-fade-up delay-2">Discover our upcoming activities, tech sessions, and massive hackathons, or browse through our past memories.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  <section class="section py-16">
    <div class="container">
      
      <!-- Upcoming Events Section -->
      <h2 class="section-title text-center scroll-reveal mb-12">Upcoming Events</h2>
      <div class="events-list">
        <!-- Placeholder for upcoming events -->
        <div class="event-card scroll-reveal delay-1" style="justify-content: center; text-align: center; padding: 4rem;">
          <div class="event-details" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;">
            <div class="icon-box" style="width: 80px; height: 80px; background: rgba(0,114,206,0.1); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #0072ce;">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" style="width: 40px; height: 40px;">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #1a1a1a;">Stay Tuned!</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #555; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto;">We are currently brewing up some amazing new events, hackathons, and sessions. Check back soon for updates!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Past Events Section -->
      <div class="mt-24">
        <h2 class="section-title text-center scroll-reveal mb-12">Past Events</h2>
        <div class="events-list">
          
          <!-- ACM Launchpad -->
          <div class="event-card scroll-reveal delay-1">
            <div class="event-date">
              <span class="day">08</span>
              <span class="month">APR '26</span>
            </div>
            <div class="event-details">
              <div class="event-badge guest-lecture">Orientation & Ideathon</div>
              <h3>ACM Launchpad</h3>
              <p>Our flagship inaugural event welcoming the new batch to the ACM chapter!</p>
              
              <div class="event-expanded-content" style="display: none; margin-top: 1rem;">
                <p>It featured an introductory ideathon where freshmen brainstormed tech solutions for campus problems. The energy was incredible with hundreds of new minds joining our community.</p>
                <div class="event-meta" style="color: #0072ce; margin-top: 1rem; padding: 1rem; background: rgba(0, 114, 206, 0.05); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 114, 206, 0.1);">
                  <span>🏆 <strong>Winners:</strong><br/>🥇 Team Alpha (1st Place)<br/>🥈 Innovators (Runner Up)</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="event-action">
              <button class="btn btn-outline read-more-btn">Read More</button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Codestorm -->
          <div class="event-card scroll-reveal delay-2">
            <div class="event-date">
              <span class="day">08</span>
              <span class="month">APR '26</span>
            </div>
            <div class="event-details">
              <div class="event-badge hackathon">Competitive Coding</div>
              <h3>Codestorm</h3>
              <p>An intense multi-hour competitive coding marathon featuring three grueling rounds: Fundamentals, Bug Solving, and DSA.</p>
              
              <div class="event-expanded-content" style="display: none; margin-top: 1rem;">
                <p>Participants battled through progressively difficult challenges. They started with programming fundamentals, advanced through a rigorous bug-solving round, and the finalists tackled complex Data Structures and Algorithms.</p>
                <div class="event-meta" style="color: #0072ce; margin-top: 1rem; padding: 1rem; background: rgba(0, 114, 206, 0.05); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 114, 206, 0.1);">
                  <span>🏆 <strong>Winners:</strong><br/>🥇 Chandrakiran (1st Place)<br/>🥈 Anwita (2nd Place)<br/>🥉 Hanu Verma (3rd Place)</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="event-action">
              <button class="btn btn-outline read-more-btn">Read More</button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Redesignx -->
          <div class="event-card scroll-reveal delay-3">
            <div class="event-date">
              <span class="day">09</span>
              <span class="month">APR '26</span>
            </div>
            <div class="event-details">
              <div class="event-badge" style="background: rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.1); color: #e91e63;">UI/UX Challenge</div>
              <h3>Redesignx</h3>
              <p>A creative 12-hour design sprint where participants completely redesigned popular apps.</p>
              
              <div class="event-expanded-content" style="display: none; margin-top: 1rem;">
                <p>Teams focused heavily on accessibility, dark mode aesthetics, and streamlining complex user journeys. The final prototypes were judged by industry design leads.</p>
                <div class="event-meta" style="color: #e91e63; margin-top: 1rem; padding: 1rem; background: rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.05); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.1);">
                  <span>🏆 <strong>Winners:</strong><br/>🥇 Team Pixel Perfect (1st Place)<br/>🥈 The Grid (Runner Up)</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="event-action">
              <button class="btn btn-outline read-more-btn">Read More</button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- AI Battle -->
          <div class="event-card scroll-reveal delay-1">
            <div class="event-date">
              <span class="day">09</span>
              <span class="month">APR '26</span>
            </div>
            <div class="event-details">
              <div class="event-badge" style="background: rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.1); color: #4caf50;">Machine Learning</div>
              <h3>AI Battle</h3>
              <p>An intense machine learning showdown to solve complex real-world datasets.</p>
              
              <div class="event-expanded-content" style="display: none; margin-top: 1rem;">
                <p>Teams competed to build, train, and deploy predictive AI models under strict time limits, dealing with messy real-world data and deploying full-stack AI pipelines.</p>
                <div class="event-meta" style="color: #4caf50; margin-top: 1rem; padding: 1rem; background: rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.05); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.1);">
                  <span>🏆 <strong>Winners:</strong><br/>🥇 Team Neural Ninjas (1st Place)<br/>🥈 Data Wizards (Runner Up)</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="event-action">
              <button class="btn btn-outline read-more-btn">Read More</button>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<script>

  function initScrollAnimations() {
    const observerOptions = {
      root: null,
      rootMargin: '0px',
      threshold: 0.1
    };

    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('in-view', 'visible');
          observer.unobserve(entry.target); 
        }
      });
    }, observerOptions);

    const revealElements = document.querySelectorAll('.scroll-reveal, .animate-fade-up');
    revealElements.forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
  }

  function initReadMore() {
    const readMoreBtns = document.querySelectorAll('.read-more-btn');
    readMoreBtns.forEach(btn => {
      // Remove old listeners to prevent duplicates on Astro page swaps
      const newBtn = btn.cloneNode(true);
      btn.parentNode.replaceChild(newBtn, btn);
      
      newBtn.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
        const card = e.target.closest('.event-card');
        const expandedContent = card.querySelector('.event-expanded-content');
        
        if (expandedContent.style.display === 'none') {
          expandedContent.style.display = 'block';
          newBtn.textContent = 'Read Less';
        } else {
          expandedContent.style.display = 'none';
          newBtn.textContent = 'Read More';
        }
      });
    });
  }

  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    initScrollAnimations();
    initReadMore();
  });
  
  document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', () => {
    initScrollAnimations();
    initReadMore();
  });
</script>

<style>
  .relative-z {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  /* --- Hero Section --- */
  .hero-section {
    position: relative;
    padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: transparent;
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 3;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 4.5rem;
    }
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #555;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }

  .py-16 { padding-top: 4rem; padding-bottom: 8rem; }
  .mt-24 { margin-top: 6rem; }
  .mb-12 { margin-bottom: 3rem; }

  /* --- Simple Animations --- */
  .animate-fade-up {
    opacity: 0;
  }
  .animate-fade-up.visible {
    animation: fadeUp 1s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
  }
  .delay-2 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* --- Event Cards --- */
  .events-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 950px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .event-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 24px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 114, 206, 0.1);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .event-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--primary-color), #00d2ff);
    transform: scaleY(0);
    transform-origin: center;
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .event-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.01);
    box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 114, 206, 0.12);
    border-color: rgba(0, 114, 206, 0.1);
  }

  .event-card:hover::before {
    transform: scaleY(1);
  }

  .event-date {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-width: 110px;
    height: 110px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 114, 206, 0.06) 0%, rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.12) 100%);
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-right: 3rem;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 114, 206, 0.1);
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
  }

  .event-card:hover .event-date {
    transform: scale(1.05) rotate(-3deg);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, #00d2ff 100%);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 114, 206, 0.2);
  }

  .event-date .day {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .event-date .month {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .event-details {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .event-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.35rem 0.85rem;
    background: rgba(0, 114, 206, 0.1);
    color: var(--primary-color);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  
  .event-badge.hackathon {
    background: rgba(156, 39, 176, 0.1);
    color: #9c27b0;
  }

  .event-badge.guest-lecture {
    background: rgba(255, 152, 0, 0.1);
    color: #f57c00;
  }

  .event-details h3 {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }

  .event-details p {
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .event-meta {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #777;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .meta-divider {
    margin: 0 0.85rem;
    color: #ccc;
  }

  .event-action {
    margin-left: 3rem;
  }

  .btn-glow {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .btn-glow::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%; left: -50%; width: 200%; height: 200%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    transform: rotate(45deg) translate(-50%, -50%);
    animation: button-shine 3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) infinite;
  }
  @keyframes button-shine {
    0% { transform: translateX(-150%) rotate(45deg); }
    30%, 100% { transform: translateX(150%) rotate(45deg); }
  }

  /* --- Scroll Reveal Animations --- */
  .scroll-reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(40px);
    transition: opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .scroll-reveal.in-view {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .delay-1 { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
  .delay-2 { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
  .delay-3 { transition-delay: 0.3s; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .event-card {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
    }
    .event-card::before {
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: auto; height: 6px; width: 100%;
      transform: scaleX(0);
    }
    .event-card:hover::before {
      transform: scaleX(1);
    }
    .event-date {
      margin-right: 0;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 140px;
    }
    .event-meta {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .meta-divider {
      display: none;
    }
    .event-action {
      margin-left: 0;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .event-action .btn {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
